  Inner loop: 1
  Inner loop: 2
  Breaking out of BOTH loops at inner=3
Outer loop: 2
  Inner loop: 1
  Inner loop: 2
  Breaking out of BOTH loops at inner=3
breaking out of both loops at outer=2
Finished!

